# Private keys are generated post-clone by secrets/regenerate-demo-identity.sh.
# OpenSSH refuses keys with mode looser than 0600, and git can't store 0600 —
# so we don't track them. Their public counterparts (.pub, recipients.nix)
# stay tracked so nix flake check works on a fresh clone.
